--- a/cm_prog.sas
+++ b/cm_prog.sas
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 1: CMDECOD is populated from raw verbatim term (CMTRT) instead of standard medication dictionary
+Fix 1: CMDECOD mapped from standard medication dictionary coding, not raw verbatim term
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 2: CMROUTE uses non-standard route codes (e.g., 'oral') instead of CDISC controlled terminology ('ORAL')
+Fix 2: CMROUTE uses CDISC controlled terminology with uppercase standard codes
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
