Summary of fixes:
1. CMDECOD mapped from standard medication dictionary coding, not raw verbatim term (medication_coding)
2. CMROUTE uses CDISC controlled terminology with uppercase standard codes (route_terminology)
3. CMSTDTC uses date-only ISO 8601 format (is8601da.) (date_format)
